body:
I can't put emoticons like ／人◕ ‿‿ ◕人＼ into my status text since it, for example, flags "人" and "◕" as offensive words that need to be removed. They were fine in the Legacy Client.

Also, the system sensors multiple normal words that I cannot think to have ANY offensive meaning.
{{sticker:zombie-brand-facepalm}}
